        h2.subtitle I make products easier to use and help businesses communicate more effectively. Below is a collection of my personal work. 


    section.case-study.case-study--days-for-girls.scene_element.scene_element--fadein(role='complementary', aria-labelledby='client')
      .case-study-information
        h2.client Days for Girls
        img.logo.lazyload(data-src='img/days-for-girls-logo.svg', alt='Days for Girls International')
        p.intro
          | Days for Girls provides girls around the world with sustainable female hygiene and health education. Facing tremendous growth, Days for Girls needed an online experience to match its programs. 
        p.view-case-study
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='case-studies/days-for-girls', onClick="ga('send', 'event', 'Contact', 'Click', 'Days for Girls Case Study', 1);") View Case Study

    section.case-study.case-study--mother-4-game.scene_element.scene_element--fadein(role='complementary', aria-labelledby='client')
      .case-study-information
        h2.client MOTHER 4
        img.logo.lazyload(data-src='http://mother4game.com/img/logo.svg', alt='Mother 4 Game')
        p.intro 
          | An indie sequel to the cult-classic video game series, Mother. Developed over two years, the video game is slated for release in summer 2015 to an active, global fanbase. 
        p.view-case-study
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='case-studies/mother-4-game', onClick="ga('send', 'event', 'Case Study', 'Click', 'Mother 4 Case Study', 1);") View Case Study

      
